{
  "stem": "16345.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a-- right smack in the central part of the United States, and we decided we wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after a stayover of several weeks in Cleveland at a-- at a-- at an orphanage, where I started learning some things academically-- there were-- I remember there was-- a professor from one of the colleges came in and started-- and started giving us math lessons.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wish I remembered some of the tricks he taught us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we went to Kansas City, and in Kansas City the social agencies helped us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They placed us with another-- with a family whose name was Tager-- T-A-G-E-R-- who had come from Germany in the early '30s, and we stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They paid them a stipend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went to high school, which wasn't-- which wasn't very easy, since my English wasn't up to par and also my knowledge was lacking.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're-- we're talking about 1948.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And I remember the-- this high school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Central High School.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was about two, three miles away from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the bus ride cost a dime, but we wanted to save money, so we would-- we would just walk and run to school to save a dime.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In those days, you could get things for a dime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then went to school over there for about six, seven months, and then I decided I got a job.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got a job-- as a matter of fact, in Germany while I was living with my aunt and uncle, my uncle had opened a fur store.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was-- he had been a furrier before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
